Go to Terminal and run below command

$ ./input.sh
$ ./run.sh
$ ./output.sh

Files detail:
Source code file: Stripes.java
Jar file: Stripes.jar
Customer data input: input.txt
Batch file put input.txt into hdfs: input.sh
Batch file to run jar file: run.sh
Batch file to get output from hdfs (part-r-00000): output.sh

